criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — framed buyer lenses and decision context (financial vs strategic, walk-away price); 
Represent — explicitly triangulated valuation approaches (DCF, trading comps, precedents); 
Implement — justified discount rate and performed sensitivity tables (WACC, terminal growth, synergies); 
Evolve/Validate — synthesized into a football-field summary and gave a recommended bid range.

Discover — framed the decision context and buyer lenses that motivate an actionable bid range; 
Implement — produced DCF results and assumptions underpinning stand‑alone value; 
Validate — applied trading comparables and precedent transactions that justify the recommended price range; 
Evolve — synthesized results into a final, executable bid recommendation.
